title: AGI- Ruger 10/22 Armorer Course
description:
Includes complete disassembly, reassembly, step-by-step design and function, and tricks to insure that you keep your gun performing at it&#039;s best. The inner working of the clever rotary magazine are revealed along with how to disassemble and clean it. Customize your rifle as we examine and demonstrate a number of accessories, including heavy target barrels, muzzle brakes, exotic magazines, custom stocks and a rare demonstration of a 10/22 "Gatling Gun" Kit. Instructor is Master Gunsmith Bob Dunlap.
